Texts.Chs: 我向往星际间的生活，请问，我可以成为你的船员吗？
Texts.Eng: A life among the stars is the one for me. Please, can I join your crew?

Texts.Chs: 好的，船长，我会在这里等你的。
有没有人感觉到宇宙最近好像一直在摇摇晃晃的？
Texts.Eng: Anyone else feel like there's been some cosmic turbulence lately?

Texts.Chs: 我可以成为你的船员吗？我可以帮到你！
Texts.Eng: Can I join you in the stars? I have skills that could help you!

Texts.Chs: 不敢相信我站在那玩意正中央的时候死了。
Texts.Eng: Can't believe I died when I was right in the middle of something.

Texts.Chs: 船长想想想要叶族人跟随？
如果你需要战斗技艺的帮助，你会在这儿找到我的。
Texts.Eng: Combat is an art, and I am an artist! I'll be here if you need me.
Do you need me to stay here?

Texts.Chs: 第一主任的第二大表亲的第三<role>
叶族人可以帮你渡渡渡过难关！
叶族人感到很很很有趣。
叶族人绝对能帮帮帮得上忙！
Texts.Eng: Floran hasss things to help you out!

Texts.Chs: 叶族人有些东西西西能帮到你！
如果你需要战斗，叶族人会帮帮帮你的！
Texts.Eng: Floran here to help you fight if you need it!

Texts.Chs: 叶族人对长期雇佣很感兴兴兴趣。你可以给我一份飞船上的工作吗？
Texts.Eng: Floran interesssted in long term employment. Can you give Floran a job?

Texts.Chs: 如果你需需需要我帮你，尽管开口，叶族人是最棒的猎猎猎人！
Texts.Eng: Floran is bessst hunter! Ask Floran if you need help some time.

Texts.Chs: 叶族人离离离你太远了！
叶族人不喜欢欢欢死亡。
Texts.Eng: Floran not a fan of dying.

Texts.Chs: 叶族人离你你你不够近！
Texts.Eng: Floran not close enough to you!

Texts.Chs: 叶族人准备好再次出出出发了！
叶族人应该待待待在这里？
叶族人被拉拉拉在后面了！
叶族人想想想要要成为你的船员！
Texts.Eng: Floran wantss to join ship crew!

Texts.Chs: 叶族人下一次会战战战斗的更好...
Texts.Eng: Floran will fight better next time...

Texts.Chs: 叶族人会待待待在这里。
叶族人会待在这里，然后...
叶族人会待在这里直到你需要叶族人去刺刺刺或是射点什么东西。
Texts.Eng: Floran will stay here until you need Floran to ssstab or shoot something.
Hey, I'm <selfname>, nice to meet ya!
Hey, biggun! Let me catch up!

Texts.Chs: 我相信我可以在旅行中帮到你。我可以成为你的船员吗？
Texts.Eng: I believe I could aid you in your travels. Perhaps I could become a crew member on your ship?

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要，我可以随时帮助你战斗！
Texts.Eng: I can always lend you my sword and skill in battle, should you need it.

Texts.Chs: 我会听从你的命令待在这里的，船长。
Texts.Eng: I can stay here if you prefer, captain.

Texts.Chs: 我会在这里等待你的下一个命令，船长。
我曾经爬上一个猿人的背，那景色真是棒极了。
Texts.Eng: I climbed an Apex once. Nice view.

Texts.Chs: 我不认为我复活的姿势很到位...
Texts.Eng: I don't think I respawned properly...

Texts.Chs: 我希望我重生时没有出什么差错，我的脸看上去还好吗？
Texts.Eng: I hope I respawned properly. Do I look alright?

Texts.Chs: 从现在起，我会一直待在这里。
Texts.Eng: I will remain here for now, then.

Texts.Chs: 船长，如果你打算让我待在这里，我会无条件地执行你的命令。
Texts.Eng: I will remain here if you want me to, captain.

Texts.Chs: 我会留守在这里，直到你需要我，船长。
Texts.Eng: I will remain on guard here until you need me, captain.

Texts.Chs: 我会待在这里，直到你需要我。
Texts.Eng: I will stay posted here until you need backup.
I wonder if this will help you?

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要我帮你战斗，请来找我，我会一直待在这里。
Texts.Eng: I'll be here for you if you need someone to help you fight bad guys!

Texts.Chs: 我会一直待在这里。直到你需要我帮你打败那些坏人。
Texts.Eng: I'll be here for you if you need someone to help you in battle.

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要人保护你，请随时吩咐，我会一直在这里的。
Texts.Eng: I'll be here if you need a warrior to defend you!

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要保镖，请来找我，我会在这里一直等你。
Texts.Eng: I'll be here if you need help to defend yourself

Texts.Chs: 我会留在这里，直到你找我帮你战斗。
Texts.Eng: I'll be waiting here big guy, come get me when it's time to fight.

Texts.Chs: 我就在这里等着，放松下我的小脚蹼。
Texts.Eng: I'll just wait here, rest my flippers.

Texts.Chs: 我会一直待在这里的，船长。
Texts.Eng: I'll stay here for now, captain.
I'll stay here for now, then.

Texts.Chs: 我就待在这里，如果你需要保护，就来找我！
Texts.Eng: I'll stay here so you know where I'll be if you need protection!

Texts.Chs: 我会一直留守的这里的。
船长，我会在这里待着，直到你需要我。
Texts.Eng: I'll stay here. Come back when you need me, captain!

Texts.Chs: 我会在这里待着，直到你需要我帮你战斗。
Texts.Eng: I'll wait here until you need me to fight something for you.

Texts.Chs: 我是一个非常有用的人！我可以加入你的队伍吗？
Texts.Eng: I'm a very useful person! Can I join you?
I'm back and in one piece!

Texts.Chs: 你在招募船员？我可以加入你的队伍吗？
Texts.Eng: I'm looking for a place among a crew. Can I join yours?

Texts.Chs: 我想找一份飞船上的活儿，你的飞船缺人吗？
Texts.Eng: I'm looking for a ship's crew to join. Are you interested?

Texts.Chs: 我想找份新的工作，请问你还需要新船员吗？
Texts.Eng: I'm looking to escape to a new life. Are you hiring?

Texts.Chs: 我觉得我的脚蹼痒痒的。
Texts.Eng: I've got an itchy trigger flipper.

Texts.Chs: 如果我成为你的船员，你是不是能保护我不受大猿人的奴役？
Texts.Eng: If I join your crew, can you protect me from Big Ape?

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要我帮助你战斗，你知道在哪里找到我！
Texts.Eng: If you need a hand in battle, you know where to find me!

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要探索之类的帮助，我会在这里等着你。
Texts.Eng: If you need assistance on your travels, I will be here.

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要与敌人战斗，我会一直待在这里！
Texts.Eng: If you need me in battle, I'll be here!

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要与敌人战斗，你知道在哪里可以找到我。
Texts.Eng: If you need me in battle, you know where I am.

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要打架，请来找我，我会一直在这里。
Texts.Eng: If you need military support, I will be here.

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要保护，你知道在哪里能找到我！
Texts.Eng: If you need protection, you know where to find me!

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要人帮你打架，请随时吩咐！
Texts.Eng: If you need someone to help you fight, I shall be here waiting!

Texts.Chs: 如果你需要关于战斗方面的帮助，请来找我。
Texts.Eng: If you need support in the art of battle, you can find me here.
Is it time to move, captain?

Texts.Chs: 无法无天，不信神的，不会飞的，这就是我！
让我来给你感受一下，什么才是真正的快！
Texts.Eng: Let me give you a boost real quick!

Texts.Chs: 看上去你需要我的帮忙！
Texts.Eng: Looks like you could use my assistance!

Texts.Chs: 我的羽毛上全粘上了枪支保养油。
Texts.Eng: My feathers are all gummed up with gun oil.

Texts.Chs: 没有自尊的企鹅和死了有什么分别。
Texts.Eng: No self-respecting penguin would stay dead for long.

Texts.Chs: 不是所有企鹅都是捣蛋鬼！前面只是句玩笑话，对，我们就是喜欢捣乱！
Texts.Eng: Not all penguins are troublemakers! Who am I kidding, yes we are.

Texts.Chs: 没有什么听起来比在星海中遨游更加振奋人心了，我可以加入你的飞船吗？
Texts.Eng: Nothing sounds as inspiring as travelling through the stars. May I join your ship?

Texts.Chs: 人人都觉得企鹅很可爱，他们想错了。
Texts.Eng: People think penguins are cute. People are wrong.

Texts.Chs: 我非常向往飞船上的生活，我可以加入你的队伍吗？
Texts.Eng: Perhaps the life aboard a ship is the one for me. Can I join you?

Texts.Chs: 我十分喜爱星际间的旅行，请问我可以成为你的船员吗？
Texts.Eng: Perhaps the life of a traveller is the one for me? May I enquire about joining your crew?

Texts.Chs: 或许这样会让你更强大一些！
Texts.Eng: Perhaps you could do with a power-up!

Texts.Chs: 重生让我的脑袋感到晕晕乎乎，不过我喜欢这种感觉。
Texts.Eng: Respawning makes my head feel fuzzy. I like it.

Texts.Chs: 拿着这个，它能帮上你的忙！
听说你在找一些船员加入你的队伍？不得不说在星海中遨游是多么美妙的一件事情...
Texts.Eng: Tell me, are you looking for crew members? Because to sail among the stars would be wonderful...

Texts.Chs: 在星海中遨游...可能你正在寻找一些得力的船员?
Texts.Eng: To sail among the stars... Perhaps you are looking for some crew members?

Texts.Chs: 我们企鹅无论发生什么事都能保持镇定。

Texts.Eng: Was I dead for a little while?
What was I doing just before I died?

Texts.Chs: 当你需要我就喊我，船长。
Texts.Eng: When you need my protection come get me, boss.

Texts.Chs: 昨天我笑到差点让鲭鱼把我的喉咙卡住了。
Texts.Eng: Yesterday I laughed so hard I almost choked on my mackerel.

Texts.Chs: 你就是我想要一起共事的人，不考虑雇用我吗?
Texts.Eng: You are JUST the kind of person I should work with! Fancy employing me?

Texts.Chs: 你有一艘飞船？可能你会想要找一些船员加入你的飞船？我怎么样？
Texts.Eng: You have a ship? Perhaps you're looking for people to join a crew?

Texts.Chs: 你看起来非常强强强壮。叶族人想要加入你的队伍！
Texts.Eng: You look ssstrong. Floran wants to join you!
